==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} {{term|corrigendum|lang=la}}, nominative neuter singular of {{term|corrigendus|lang=la}}, the future passive participle (gerundive) of {{term|corrigo|corrigō|I correct|lang=la}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|corrigend|a}}

# An [[error]] that is to be [[correct]]ed in a [[print]]ed work after [[publication]].
# {{usually|plural}} A [[list]] of errors in a printed work as a separate page of [[correction]]s, known as an [[errata]] page.

